## DOOR TRIM REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


1. Remove the regulator handle if equipped with manual window. (Refer to 09-12 REGULATOR HANDLE REMOVAL.) (Refer to 09-12 REGULATOR HANDLE INSTALLATION.) 
2. Remove the screw. 
3. Remove the inner handle cover. 
4. Remove the fasteners.  


5. Pull the door trim to disengage the clips A and B from the body. 
6. Lift the door trim to disengage hooks C and D from the body.  

![](images/1.jpg)
  


7. Install in the reverse order of removal.